Package: scLean
Type: Package
Title: Memory-Efficient Single-Cell RNA-seq Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-05-18
Authors@R: c(
    person("rzyang-dev", email = "ruizhe.yang@foxmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")))
Author: rzyang-dev
Maintainer: rzyang-dev <ruizhe.yang@foxmail.com>
Description: A memory-efficient single-cell RNA-seq analysis package that
    replaces Seurat's core functionality with disk-backed (HDF5) computation.
    Designed to run complete scRNA-seq pipelines (normalization, scaling, PCA,
    clustering, differential expression) on commodity hardware with 8GB RAM for
    datasets of 500K+ cells. Uses C++ with Rcpp for performance and HDF5 for
    out-of-core storage.
License: GPL (>= 3)
